data.description: Great tastefully updated North Tacoma home. Kitchen flooring bathrooms etc...  The home would be perfect for a multi generation house, home office, home school, or home business. Rent rooms? Lots of options. A huge kitchen that includes an island and double oven for the entertainer or baker in you. Also, a large dry, partially unfinished basement. The finished part of the basement is perfect for storage for all the seasonal decorations. There are also separate living quarters with 3/4 bath within the house. 2 blocks from the local park that has a large field to walk the dog or use the 2-baseball fields to play some pick-up games or practice. Very walkable area. Close to Ruston Way and the farmers market, restaurants, and waterfront parks.
